QuestData.Title: More Marks of Kil'jaeden
QuestData.CompletionText: Do you bear more of our enemies' insignias, $C? The Burning Legion continues to be a threat and we continue to pursue them anywhere that we find them.
QuestData.RewardText: You continue to prove your worth, $N. Fight the enemies of the Light wherever you may find them; your actions will be well-rewarded.
